/*** how to make my .js file a script */

Step1: add following to the first line of the .js file

#! /usr/bin/env node


Step2: Turn the script into an npm project (if not already an npm project) by putting it into its own folder then running npm init inside that folder (this will create a package.json file)

Step3: Edit the package.json file and add a bin property

"bin" : {
    "your-script" : "./your-script.js"
}

step4: Run npm link in the directory